# Affiliate Blog Platform — Implementation Plan
## MERN Stack + Tailwind CSS + Cloudinary

A production-ready Affiliate Blog Platform with a Deep Black / Matrix Green "Tech-Minimalist" theme, Glassmorphism card UI, full admin dashboard, and SEO optimization. Deployable to **Render** (server) + **Vercel** (client) + **MongoDB Atlas**.

